cat << EOF
PLIB is a set of libraries to write games and other realtime interactive
applications that are 100% portable across a wide range of hardware and
operating systems. It's used by Majik3D, FlightGear, and others, and
includes libraries for GUI widgets, sound replay, geometry, scene graph,
joystick, and fonts/text.
